description:
Created for the Dome Keeper 2025 Mod Jam!  

Want more resources?  
More complicated upgrades?  
Crafting?  
We have it all!  

This mod adds new resources, crafting, and changes the upgrade tree for the Laser Weapon.  
Have fun!  

Note: This mod will be incompatible with mods that also add resources.
name: MoreToMine
